# Line-ending policy: LF-canonical. Everything in this repo ships to or runs on
# Linux (pkg0 itself, packaging/postinst, scripts/install.sh — all bash/sh, and
# CRLF breaks a shebang). eol=lf overrides core.autocrlf=true on Windows checkouts
# so the working tree always matches the LF blobs.
* text=auto eol=lf
